{"id":452650781,"lang":"cpp","time":"1 year, 6 months","timestamp":1612598075,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"8 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/452650781/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Roman to Integer","memory":"5.8 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int romanToInt(string s) {\n        int value=0;\n        for(int i=0;i<s.size();i++)\n        {\n            if(s.at(i)=='I')\n                value++;\n            else if(s.at(i)=='V')\n            {\n                value+=5;\n                if(i!=0 && s.at(i-1)=='I')\n                    value-=2;\n            }\n            else if(s.at(i)=='X')\n            {\n                value+=10;\n                if(i!=0 && s.at(i-1)=='I')\n                    value-=2;\n            }\n            else if(s.at(i)=='L')\n            {\n                value+=50;\n                if(i!=0 && s.at(i-1)=='X')\n                    value-=20;\n            }\n            else if(s.at(i)=='C')\n            {\n                value+=100;\n                if(i!=0 && s.at(i-1)=='X')\n                    value-=20;\n            }\n            else if(s.at(i)=='D')\n            {\n                value+=500;\n                if(i!=0 && s.at(i-1)=='C')\n                    value-=200;\n            }\n            else if(s.at(i)=='M')\n            {\n                value+=1000;\n                if(i!=0 && s.at(i-1)=='C')\n                    value-=200;\n            }\n        }\n        return value;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"roman-to-integer"}
